job_history.work_description: Provided maintenance support to TWPC. Effective communicator and leader in the work areas.
Prepared and shipped about 250 metric tons worth of military equipment on numerous operations to countries such as Australia, Thailand and Guam.
Operated on and repaired around 200 pieces of gear used in F-18 fighter jets, EA-6B Electronic counter-measures jets, or AV-8B close ground support jets.
